                        <div class="section-tittle section-tittle2">
                            <span>What we are doing</span>
                            <h2>24k Talented people are getting Jobs</h2>
                        </div>
                        <div class="support-caption">
                            <p class="pera-top">New World Employment Services, located in the heart of Kathmandu, Nepal, is dedicated to enriching the professional landscape by providing unparalleled opportunities for both job seekers and employers. Our mission is to act as the catalyst for professional growth in Kathmandu, fostering seamless connections between talent and opportunity through cutting-edge technological solutions and unwavering dedication. We envision a future where every individual in Kathmandu is empowered to achieve their career aspirations, fueled by our commitment to innovation and inclusivity. Our core values of empowerment, integrity, and innovation drive our comprehensive services, including job placement across diverse industries, personalized career development guidance, and tailored recruitment solutions for employers. Join us in shaping a dynamic employment ecosystem that nurtures talent, fosters collaboration, and fuels progress for generations to come.</p>

